{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712@2.pkg/1772602086961/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602088069", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712@2.pkg/1772602086961/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602088069"}, "identifier": "c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>【解析】D.有误，“叙事诗”错。《蒹葭》是抒情诗，抒发的是追求所爱而不及的惆怅与苦闷之情。</p>\n\n<p>【答案】D</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列对《蒹葭》的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "下列对《蒹葭》的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712@2.pkg/item.json?v=1753065821745", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>全诗分为三章，每章前两句以凄清冷漠的景致起兴，形成一种沉郁悲凉的氛围，同时又暗寓了时间的推移。后六句描写访求“伊人”而未得的迷惘之情。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“在水一方”“宛在水中央”“宛在水中沚”是说伊人所在的地方有流水环境，仿佛置身于洲岛上，可望而不可及。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>“伊人”是诗人访求的对象，是美的化身，在诗人矢志不渝的追求中，犹如强烈地感受到了那“在水一方”的倩影。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>这首诗描写了“伊人”生活的环境和诗人在不同时间不懈地寻找“伊人”的过程。因此，从诗的内容看，它应是一首叙事诗。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列对《蒹葭》的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对《蒹葭》的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列对《蒹葭》的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2465d6c-ac11-4669-8e00-1280bb634712@2.pkg/1772602086961/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602088069", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c2465d